# Los Necios Desktop

Official desktop installers for Los Necios — privacy-first AI tools.

## Download

Get the latest version from [Releases →](https://github.com/losnecios-apps/Los-Necios-Platform-Releases/releases)

### Supported Platforms
- macOS 10.15+ (Universal — Intel & Apple Silicon)
- Windows 10/11
- Linux (x86_64 AppImage)

## Installation

### macOS
1. Download `Los-Necios-x.x.x-universal.dmg`
2. Open the DMG
3. Drag **Los Necios** to Applications
4. Launch from Applications folder

### Windows
1. Download `Los-Necios-Setup-x.x.x.exe`
2. Run the installer
3. Launch from Start Menu

### Linux
1. Download `Los-Necios-x.x.x.AppImage`
2. Make executable: `chmod +x Los-Necios-x.x.x.AppImage`
3. Run: `./Los-Necios-x.x.x.AppImage`

